canada-56620113|dead-url=no}}</ref>。行凶者是25岁的诺亚·格林（Noah Green），衝撞警察後，他一边挥舞着刀子一边下车<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|author=Olson|first=Tyler|author2=Phillips|first2=Morgan|title=Capitol police officer dead, another wounded after car rams into barrier; suspect killed|url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/capitol-locked-down-due-to-exterior-security-threat|work=Fox News|date=April 2, 2021|accessdate=April 2, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210402211151/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/capitol-locked-down-due-to-exterior-security-threat|dead-url=no}}</ref>，無視警方警告並朝警员扑去。此時其他警员向诺亚·格林开枪<ref>{{Cite web|title=1 officer dead, 1 injured after car rams Capitol barrier; suspect fatally shot|url=https://thehill.com/policy/national-security/546197-capitol-locked-down-due-to-security-incident|accessdate=2021-04-02|author=Lonas|date=2021-04-02|first=Lexi|work=The Hill|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403125249/https://thehill.com/policy/national-security/546197-capitol-locked-down-due-to-security-incident|dead-url=no}}</ref>。诺亚·格林中槍後被逮捕，最終因伤势过重，在送医後宣告不治<ref name="NYT.Follower">{{Cite news|first=Ben|author=Decker|first2=Adam|author2=Goldman|first3=Zolan|last3=Kanno-Youngs|title=Suspect in Capitol attack appears to have been a follower of Louis Farrakhan.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/04/02/us/noah-green-farrakhan.html|accessdate=2 April 2021|work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|date=2 April 2021|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403083802/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/04/02/us/noah-green-farrakhan.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NBC.Rammed">{{Cite news|title=U.S. Capitol Police officer dies after attacker rammed car into checkpoint; suspect also dead|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/suspect-custody-after-car-rams-two-officers-u-s-capitol-n1262917|work=NBC News|date=April 2, 2021|accessdate=April 2, 2021|language=en|author=Gregorian|first=Dareh|author2=Caldwell|first2=Leigh Ann|last3=Dienst|first3=Jonathan|archive-date=2021-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403122351/https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/suspect-custody-after-car-rams-two-officers-u-s-capitol-n1262917|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|first=Zachary|author=Cohen|first2=Lauren|author2=Fox|first3=Jessica|last3=Dean|first4=David|last4=Shortell|title=Capitol Police officer killed, another injured after suspect rams car into police barrier outside building|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/04/02/politics/us-capitol-incident/index.html|work=CNN|date=April 2, 2021|accessdate=April 2, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403055818/https://www.cnn.com/2021/04/02/politics/us-capitol-incident/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 襲擊者 ==
嫌疑人诺亚·格林（Noah Green）是一名来自[[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]]的25岁[[非裔美国人|非裔美国]]男子<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Suspect involved in Capitol incident identified as 25 year old man from Indiana|url=https://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/watch/suspect-involved-in-capitol-incident-identified-as-25-year-old-man-from-indiana-109579845654|accessdate=2021-04-02|date=April 2, 2021|work=MSNBC|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403122200/https://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/watch/suspect-involved-in-capitol-incident-identified-as-25-year-old-man-from-indiana-109579845654|dead-url=no}}</ref>，和他一起上学的人曾表示他平時喜愛運動。其他认识诺亚·格林的人看到他在[[Facebook|Facebook]]上曾发布一些支持[[伊斯兰民族|伊斯兰民族]]及其前领导人[[路易斯·法拉堪|路易斯·法拉堪]]的帖子<ref>{{Cite web|title=Suspect in attack at U.S. Capitol went from jock to posting about paranoia, extremist groups|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/04/02/noah-green-went-from-football-player-posting-extremist-groups/7068100002/|accessdate=2021-04-03|author=Hayes|first=Christal|work=USA TODAY|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403113646/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2021/04/02/noah-green-went-from-football-player-posting-extremist-groups/7068100002/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYT.Follower" />，诺亚·格林還表示[[美國政府|美國政府]]是黑人的頭號公敵<ref>{{cite news |title=非裔男開車衝撞美國會　稱政府「黑人頭號敵人」 |url=https://news.tvbs.com.tw/politics/1487779}}</ref>。

